quran[9{c,v,t}:
27,36,"jab woh ( malka ka safeer ) sulaiman ke haan pouncha to is ne kaha"" kya tum log maal se meri madad karna chahtay ho? jo kuch khuda ne mujhe day rakha hai woh is se bohat ziyada hai jo tumhe diya hai tumhara Hadia tumhi ko mubarak rahay"
27,37,"( ae safeer ) wapas ja apne bhejnay walon ki taraf hum un par aisay lashkar le kar ayen ge jin ka muqaabla woh nah kar saken ge aur hum inhen aisi zillat ke sath wahan se nikalen ge ke woh khawar ho kar reh jayen ge """
27,38,"sulaiman ne kaha"" “اay ahal darbaar, tum mein se kon is ka takhat mere paas lata hai qabal is ke ke woh log Mutee ho kar mere paas haazir hon? """
27,39,"junoo mein se aik quwwat hekal ne arz kya"" mein usay haazir kar dun ga qabal is ke ke aap apni jagah se utheen mein is ki taaqat rakhta hon aur amanatdar hon """
27,40,"jis shakhs ke paas kitaab ka ilm tha woh bola"" mein aap ki palak jhapkane se pehlay usay laaye deta hon"" jounhi ke sulaiman ne woh takhat apne paas rakha howa dekha, woh pukaar utha"" yeh mere rab ka fazl hai taakay woh mujhe aazamaa_e ke mein shukar karta hon ya kafir Nemat ban jata hon aur jo koi shukar karta hai is ka shukar is ke apne hi liye mufeed hai, warna koi nashukri kere to mera rab be niaz aur apni zaat mein aap buzurag hai """
27,41,"sulaiman ne kaha"" anjaan tareeqay se is ka takhat is ke samnay rakh do, dekhen woh sahih baat taq pahunchti hai ya unn logon mein se hai jo raah e raast nahi paate """
27,42,"malka jab haazir hui to is se kaha gaya kya tera takhat aisa hi hai? woh kehnay lagi"" yeh to goya wohi hai hum to pehlay hi jaan gay thay aur hum ne sar-e itaat jhuka diya tha ( ya hum muslim ho chuke thay ) """
27,43,"uss ko ( imaan laane se ) jis cheez ne rok rakha tha woh unn mabodon ki ibadat thi jinhein woh Allah ke siwa پوجتی thi, kyunkay woh aik kafir qoum se thi"
27,44,"is se kaha gaya ke mehal mein daakhil ho is ne jo dekha to samjhi ke pani ka hoz hai aur utrney ke liye is ne apne painchay utha liye sulaiman ne kaha yeh sheeshay ka chikna farsh hai is par woh pukaar uthi"" ae mere rab, ( aaj taq ) mein apne nafs par bara zulm karti rahi, aur ab mein ne sulaiman ke sath Allah rab alameen ki itaat qubool kar li """
